{"tid":1296039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊貼文批評有人以誣衊方式要求他人認錯辭職","createTime":"2019-07-08T08:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T08:40:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d992036130d290c97fbd2a5c83134a3223f126e","tid":1296039,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員湯家驊於社交網站貼文表示，社會上有人會先堆砌一些虛假事實，誣衊公眾人物，然後要求公眾人物認錯甚至辭職，認為如果有關人士認錯辭職，等同確認虛砌的指控，若不認錯辭職，又會被指死不認錯，認為現在有一種極不健康和極不負責任的風氣。<br />\n<br />\n自由黨榮譽主席田北俊早前表示，聯同黨內另外3名榮譽主席去信黨主席張宇人，要求他辭去行政會議成員一職，又認為湯家驊及另一名行政會議成員葉劉淑儀亦要辭任行會成員。"},{"pid":"f870a06358ed73745aabc68693a43863dedb2fc0","tid":1296039,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1467216_1_L_20190708160113.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1467216_1_L_20190708160113.jpg&h=82b0d735&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6899d032f8a79100bc57a128d05c44a9a4e50b5a","tid":1296039,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">淚</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c2c6fe34092875394e57a4ec02c64d8dc7981530","tid":1296039,"uid":43133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:37:30.000Z","msg":"十一哥嬲嬲豬呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36302f4f01f48b7cc4f811dc473b3facc67034e4","tid":1296039,"uid":131717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:37:40.000Z","msg":"十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5b7781be69fc44075b85ba3efd2aa3607f782c","tid":1296039,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T08:38:04.000Z","msg":"佢自己衰十一都未認錯！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\